Taylor Swift" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-2009vmas.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-2009vmas-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-2009vmas-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-2009vmas-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-2009vmas-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-2009vmas-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3834517" class="wp-caption-text"> Kanye West accepts the Video Vanguard Award from Taylor Swift onstage during the 2015 MTV Video Music Awards 2015. CREDIT: Kevin Winter/MTV1415/Getty Images For MTV)</figcaption></figure><p> During Swift&#39;s speech for winning Best Music Video at the awards show, West interrupted the then 19-year-old to announce: “Yo, Taylor, I&#39;m really happy for you, I&#39;mma let you finish, but <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">Beyoncé</a> had one of the best videos of all time!有史以来最好的视频之一！” <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-762-1310187">West apologised shortly afterwards to Swift</a> .</p><p> He initially condemned his actions, by stating: “I would not want some crazy drunk rock star cutting my daughter off also.” However, he seemingly backtracked with the admission that: “ <a href="http://www.eonline.com/news/475430/kanye-west-reflects-on-taylor-swift-incident-i-wouldn-t-want-a-crazy-drunk-rock-star-cutting-off-my-daughter">My daughter would 100-percent also be like, &#39;Yes Beyonce did have the best video</a> .&#39; That&#39;s what my daughter would do.” </p><figure id="attachment_3833890" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3833890" style="width: 1392px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3833890" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/KanyeWes