 feud with the reality TV personality</a> about <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-and-kanye-wests-infamous-phone-call-has-been-leaked-online-2632983">when the phone call she had with West to discuss &#39;Famous&#39; leaked online</a> , saying it “took me down psychologically to a place I&#39;ve never been before”.</p><p> Swift also made headlines following the 2025 Grammys, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-think-taylor-swift-and-billie-eilish-were-robbed-at-2025-grammys-3834191">as fans were shocked to find she walked away empty handed</a> – the first time the star has ever been snubbed when she had six or more nominations.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-shares-that-he-now-follows-taylor-swift-on-instagram-3834487">Kanye West shares that he now follows Taylor Swift on Instagram</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
